_sText:
My first map. It is made up of five levels, the last three being connected by a sort of "door room". You must go through the doors in the correct order, in order to go on to the next level(red, white, then blue). 
Thx Dream for the packing tip.

Edit: Thanks for all the feedback from everyone :] If I end up making another map I'll spend more time on the details, and get more suggestions from playtesters.
